'''High King''' was a title used by a ruler who had at least nominal overlordship over other realms:
* [[High King (Dúnedain)|High King]], a title used by the Kings of all the [[Dúnedain]].
* [[King of Arda|High King of Arda]], a title of [[Manwë]], the greatest of the [[Valar]].
* [[King of Arnor|High King of Arnor]], a title used by the rulers of [[Arnor]].
* [[High King of the Elves]], the title of [[Ingwë]] as the noblest of all the [[Elves]].
* [[High King of the Noldor]], a title used by the four leaders of the [[Noldor]] in [[Middle-earth]].
